  "body": "I am very glad that the txpool_contentFrom method has been supported so far, which can filter the transactions in the memory pool according to the from address, but it will be more useful to add the txpool_contentTo RPC method. In many cases, it is necessary to filter the transactions in the memory pool according to the to address. I really hope to add this interface, thanks!",
