    "body": "I don't think that's really useful. Transactions can have arbitrary nestings and I'd assume you'd be interested in all txs that touch a contract, not only those that directly call into a contract on the topmost call. We can't give you all the nested calls without executing the code, and even then it would depend on the order, so it wouldn't really be meaningful either.",
